; DMARC Record (Domain-based Message Authentication, Reporting & Conformance)
_dmarc  IN      TXT     "v=DMARC1; p=quarantine; rua=mailto:dmarc-reports@example.com; ruf=mailto:dmarc-reports@example.com; fo=1"
